{"tid":522021,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我應唔應該投周庭一票?","createTime":"2018-01-07T07:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T09:03:31.000Z","uid":143499,"like":130,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a68a3c8734cf5709f76355817b032273499ea6a4","tid":522021,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"大家唔好屌我住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我本人好憎學民思潮同香港中箭，又吃人血杯麵，條數又未完全交代，本身諗住我嗰票射落海都唔俾泛民、 中箭、張秀賢( 上次畀熱血公民班仆街呃咗去幫射撚滿助選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )。 但係諗深一層， 周庭要出嚟選係因為佢哋畀人DQ， 雖然唔好唔甘心但係佢哋上次真係贏咗個選舉。<br />\n如果我基於公義投呢一票畀佢哋， 又會唔會違反咗我嘅政治取向呢？<br />\n簡單嚟講我想投佢嘅原因係因為羅37上次贏咗，呢一席係應得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再加上今次又冇本土派參加， 還返佢哋畀人DQ嗰一席畀佢哋咁又啱唔啱呢？<br />\n<br />\n我個人今次唔算含淚投泛民， 因為我投依一票唔係支持佢嘅政治理念， 亦唔係為咗保住所謂既關鍵一席，而係基於政府夾硬褫奪佢哋嘅資格， 物歸原主啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以投周庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打死都唔投周庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2e4f0bc961770a0fcb660052055ca85720f77a","tid":522021,"uid":143499,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:16:54.000Z","msg":"屈我係五毛嗰啲契弟可以收皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日冇興趣同你班支那賤種討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63aa950410735454c9c8da08de0b728dbe54f27","tid":522021,"uid":143499,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:20:59.000Z","msg":"屌，講正經嘢冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講淘寶、花生嘢、 同埋淫賤嘢就咁多人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4ccc616233acbab35df6b6dedffd33d7b29e7a","tid":522021,"uid":50188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:22:34.000Z","msg":"有得投咪投，除非你決心要焦土"},{"pid":"b40da3d1e94f0a1a9bc0625428704e501be76027","tid":522021,"uid":143499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3f4ccc616233acbab35df6b6dedffd33d7b29e7a","tid":522021,"uid":50188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:22:34.000Z","msg":"有得投咪投，除非你決心要焦土"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"我純粹係想還番一席畀佢， 純粹出於公義"},{"pid":"8176f4114f54a4e526391f027f80ad74e1eb9624","tid":522021,"uid":34394,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"你以為俾番佢係公義，其實只係令到個社會更加唔公義<br />\n<br />\n政黨公義&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;社會公義"},{"pid":"71e259f46f7d124408ed6fc2e3d4d581c83e2539","tid":522021,"uid":143499,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"8176f4114f54a4e526391f027f80ad74e1eb9624","tid":522021,"uid":34394,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"你以為俾番佢係公義，其實只係令到個社會更加唔公義<br />\n<br />\n政黨公義&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;社會公義"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"問題係即使佢哋咁仆街但係都咁多人選， 我哋係咪應該尊重反選民嘅意向呢？<br />\n我認為我哋應該尊重返上次選舉嘅結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我哋當所有唔支持本土嘅選民唔係選民咁我哋同共產黨有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4ea1f9cffb9968e26d423da40964929bf66653","tid":522021,"uid":72688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"諗緊"},{"pid":"9a5101e614179b9dc0b352b383350308b95dc30d","tid":522021,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"71e259f46f7d124408ed6fc2e3d4d581c83e2539","tid":522021,"uid":143499,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"8176f4114f54a4e526391f027f80ad74e1eb9624","tid":522021,"uid":34394,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"你以為俾番佢係公義，其實只係令到個社會更加唔公義<br />\n<br />\n政黨公義&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;社會公義"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"問題係即使佢哋咁仆街但係都咁多人選， 我哋